For brands which have light and dark mode support, you can enable them via the `data-theme` attribute.

#### NOTE: Dark Mode has been disabled for this release and switching to dark mode will not do anything.

Available theme values:

- light (default)
- dark

```html
<StaticCode language="jsx" code={`
<div data-brand="wbc" data-theme="dark">
  <!-- Your app content -->
</div>
`} />
```
